channel.title: Font Installer
channel.description:
I was digging through my old vb projects and i found this, its a font installer all you need to do is find a font you like on http://www.1001fonts.com/ and it will search for the download link download it then asks you if you want to install now or get more fonts. ill add some pictures in a minute but heres a v scan to prove its clean (it only says its a virus on 1 anti-virus because it downloads files and moves them to another part of your pc)
Scan: http://scanner.novirusthanks.org/analysis/68398310333db7923a5b6a10298ff528/Rm9udF9JbnN0YWxsZXIuZXhl/
Download: http://uppit.com/3dfrtt9l618i/Font_Installer.exe
THIS ONLY WORKS ON VISTA AND UPWARD
